Package: kalinova
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-pyqt6, python3-sklearn, python3-jinja2, python3-yaml, nmap, nikto, john, hydra
Maintainer: Kalinova Team <kalinova@example.com>
Description: Intelligent GUI Security Suite for Kali Linux
 Kalinova provides terminal-free GUI wrappers for Kali Linux
 security tools with ML-powered next-step suggestions.
 Designed for cybersecurity students and beginners.
